e used to prevent the library from being enqueued</li><li>Core: Added new <code>enqueue_google_maps</code> setting which can be used to prevent the library from being enqueued</li><li>Core: Minor fixes and improvements</li><li>Language: Updated Portuguese translation - thanks to Pedro Mendonca</li><li>Language: Updated Norwegian translation - thanks to Havard Grimelid</li><li>Language: Updated Swedish translation - thanks to Jonathan de Jong</li><li>Language: Updated German translation - thanks to Ralf Koller</li><li>Language: Updated Italian translation - thanks to Davide Pantè</li><li>Language: Updated Swiss German translation - thanks to Raphael Hüni</li></ul>";s:14:"upgrade_notice";s:0:"";}', 'no'),
