e for Blog, Portfolio or Ecommerce site.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/esquare-responsive-wordpress-blog-theme/13895642" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Esquare</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Bellevue</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Perfect for your vacation rental or hotel. Includes a full booking system, availability calendar and payments through WooCommerce.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/bellevue-hotel-bed-breakfast-booking-theme/12482898" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Bellevue</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">GDayNews</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Blog and Magazine WordPress theme</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.jawtemplates.com/jaw-portfolio/gdn-magazine-blog-video-theme/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase GDayNews</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Kaleidoscope</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Kaleidoscope is a beautiful and easy-to-use, grid-style theme optimized for WordPress food blogs.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://lazycatthemes.com/kaleidoscope/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Kaleidoscope</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Hello Friday</h2>\n<blockquote><p>A beautiful, lifestyle blog theme for creatives, travellers, photographers, foodies, professionals or story tellers.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/hello-friday-elegant-lifestyle-blog-theme/17695139" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Hello Friday</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Focuson</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Fully Responsive and Retina-Ready clean and flexible WordPress Theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/focuson-business-wordpress-theme/15611214" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Focuson</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Labomba</h2>\n<blockquote><p>LABOMBA is a WooComerce based template for your fashion website.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/labomba-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/6106367" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Labomba</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">KnowAll</h2>\n<blockquote><p>KnowAll offers self-service support, with a knowledge base customers can help themselves without having to raise a support tickets.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://herothemes.com/themes/knowall-wordpress-knowledge-base/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase KnowAll</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Basic</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Basic is fully responsive, clean and minimal WordPress theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://wordpress.org/themes/basic/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Download Basic</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Minishop</h2>\n<blockquote><p>MiniShop is a HTML5/CSS3/Bootstrap optimized responsive, minimal theme perfect for multi-purpose e-Commerce websites</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/minishop-multipurpose-minimal-ecommerce-marketplace-wordpress-theme/17507806" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Minishop</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-al