(2166, 317, 'wpcf-unigolf-e-handicap', 'With only few clicks, now golfers can update your points, manage and monitor Handicap score not only for yourselves but also your friends right now on your laptop (with Internet connection).\r\n\r\neHanicap system is very precise and certified worldwide could be found at our website UniGolf with a yearly rate <strong>only 300.000 VND</strong>. This rate include opening account fee at UniGolf and support fee via email, phone.\r\n\r\nFor account registration to start caculate your Handicap, golfers please send your information via this below form to UniGolf at <b><a href="mailto:handicap@unigolf.vn?subject=Handicap">handicap@unigolf.vn</a></b>\r\n\r\n<strong>Full name:</strong></br>\r\n<strong>Email:</strong></br>\r\nPhone number:</br>\r\nHome/office address:</br>\r\n\r\n<strong>and your request to use eHandicap of UniGolf</strong></br>\r\n\r\nUniGolf will reply you with <strong>password and account</strong> to sign-in eHanicap system. From this, golfers can start activate all options available on eHandicap system.\r\n\r\nClick here to start use eHandicap:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFor eHanicap payment fee using, please make your payment through this bank account:\r\n\r\nName of account: Nguyễn Ngọc Bảo</br>\r\n\r\nAccount number: 0071000803758</br>\r\n\r\nVietcombank - Ho Chi Minh Branch</br>\r\n\r\nPlease write the transfer content with this: <strong>ehandicap payment fee- [your full name]</strong>\r\n\r\nIf you have any problems when registration or using, please contact us via:</br>\r\n\r\n<strong>Hotline: 0909 362 655 (Ms. Anna)</strong></br>\r\n\r\n<strong>Email: handicap@unigolf.vn</strong></br>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://admin.unigolf.vn/Uploads/Article/nhap%20diem.jpg" alt="UniGolf handicap" />'),
(2167, 317, 'wpcf-announcement', 'Announcement: eHANDICAP SYSTEM NOW ONLINE ON UNIGOLF WEBSITE 2015-2016\r\n\r\nDear registered users of eHandicap system from UniGolf,</br>\r\n\r\nAt first, UniGolf want to thank all golfers who trust and start using eHandicap system from UniGolf and hope all of you satisfy with this system.</br>\r\n\r\nRight now the system is already out-of-date and UniGolf start receiving new registration as well as upgrading it to serve you better. From 01/06/2015 to 30/5/2016, UniGolf will charge a small amount of money to all users for maintaining the system and a team supporting you:</br>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #2e4070;"><strong>300,000 VND/1 year (from the day you activate the account)</strong></span></br>\r\n\r\nYour old account is still available and can update new score to it. All the information is secured\r\n\r\nAfter receiving the using fee, UniGolf staff will send you Club name, new account and password\r\n\r\nWe truly value your loyal to UniGolf and hope you will continue to support us!</br>\r\n\r\n<b>Bank account for fee payment:</b>\r\nAccount number: 0071000803758</br>\r\nAccount name: Nguyễn Ngọc Bảo</br>\r\nVietcombank - branch Hồ Chí Minh</br>\r\n\r\nPayment details: handicap fee – [full name of user]'),
