(2, 1, '2016-11-14 00:56:13', '2016-11-14 00:56:13', '<strong>A right-hand man for any golfers</strong>\r\n\r\nUnited Golf Services Company (UniGolf) was established and operated by Mr Jamie Bao Nguyen – a leading golfers in Vietnam with 15 years of experience in golfing and working in USA. In additional, our staff at UniGolf are knowledgeable and skillful in order to satisfy any demands or needs from the customers. We are very confident in providing customers with only the best and professional services for not only individual but also organizations, industry partners in Vietnam and all over the world.\r\n\r\n<strong>What services and products do UniGolf offer?</strong>\r\n\r\nDon’t have to think twice when looking for a suppliers who can provide any golf services, UniGolf is here to help you. Let’s take a look to what we will can offer to you at this websites and if you have any needs or demands, just tell us and we will make it happened\r\n\r\n<img src="http://images.unigolf.vn/Uploads/Article/bannermail-Recovered.png" alt="UniGolf Vietnam Golf Tourism" />\r\n\r\n<strong>1. Best rate booking tee time for all golf courses in Vietnam</strong>\r\n\r\nUniGolf provide booking tee time service for all golf courses in Vietnam with the best and most competitive rate you ever had. Free consultation with hotline: +84 909 344 653, we always listen and readily to handle any requests from customers. Best rate for Vietnam golf courses for preference <u>here</u>\r\n\r\n<strong>2. Inbound &amp; Outbound Travel</strong>\r\n\r\nUniGolf is an official members of IAGTO (International Association of Golf Tour Operators) and agent for golf courses, hotel, etc throughout the country. We provide service with quality and reasonable price for domestic and international tour operators from leisure tours to golf travel packages, or family holidays to corporate tours. Besides, we also offer other travel services 24/7 such as:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Accommodation booking: hotel, resorts, etc in Vietnam and all over the world</li>\r\n 	<li>Flight tickets booking</li>\r\n 	<li>Car rental for private transportation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>3. Golf events organization</strong>\r\n\r\nUniGolf always listen to every demands and needs from customers and will recommend you with the best advices for your events base on our skill and years of hosting such events. We understand that for every events is an important milestone to each customers, therefore we pay a lots of attentions and take care to every details in order to make your event successful. Contact us now for events like:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Business events: opening ceremony, product launch event, corporate anniversary,etc</li>\r\n 	<li>Workshop, convention, meeting, contract signing ceremony</li>\r\n 	<li>Golf tournament for clubs or groups</li>\r\n 	<li>Golf business tournaments leagues for brand promotions, customer gratitude</li>\r\n 	<li>Business events plus golf tournament</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>4. ProShop and Indoor Golf Simulators</strong>\r\n\r\nUniGolf Shop and our online store always update newest golf products &amp; golf equipment from major brands like TaylorMade, Nike, Footjoy, Titleist, Honma, Mizuno, Puma, etc in order to supply golfers only the most stylish yet high quality tools for the games when you go to the courses. We will advise you on what should to buy and delivering on time for products like:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Golf clubs (whole set or single) for male, female, children with different ages</li>\r\n 	<li>Golf equipment</li>\r\n 	<li>Golf clothes, shoes, accessories</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nUniGolf is exclusive agency of TruGolf, Par T Golf distributing modern Indoor Golf Simulators inclduing installament on golfer''s house\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>UniGolf Partners</strong>\r\n\r\nMore than 35 golf courses in Vietnam and all over the world\r\n\r\nMore than 2000 hotel &amp; resorts from the inexpensive to the most luxury in Vietnam\r\n\r\nInternational &amp; domestic airliners\r\n\r\nMore than 1000 partners who are tour operators, golf courses associations, golf courses, resort of more than 100 nations in IAGTO (International Association of Golf Tour Operators)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>UniGolf Customers</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://images.unigolf.vn/Uploads/Article/LOGOPARTNER-ALL-1.png" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Award</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><img class="aligncenter" src="http://images.unigolf.vn/Uploads/Article/12(13)(1).jpg" alt="" width="462" height="760" /></strong>\r\n\r\nUnited golf services received vietnam''s best inbound golf tour operator 2015 award. Being part of world travel award, the world golf award serves to celebrate and reward excellence in golf tourism through our annual awards progammes. Winning this award is also the contributions of many partners in golf industry in Vietnam and therefore we thank you all for offer us the most competitive rate in the market. We promise to ourselves to work harder and improve more to keep this title for our company not in this year but for many years to come in the future.\r\n<div></div>\r\n<em>UniGolf always place customer’s satisfaction above all when supplying our products or services. We always hope to receive your ideas and thoughts so if you have anything regarding golf or travel, please don’t hesitate contact us via:</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter" src="http://admin.unigolf.vn/Uploads/Article/Unitgolf.jpg" alt="" width="328" height="521" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><b>Headquarters:</b></td>\r\n<td><b>1437 Nguyen Van Linh, Tan Phong Ward, District 7, HCMC</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>HCM Branch:</td>\r\n<td>84-86 Tan Son Street, Ward 15, Tan Binh District, HCMC</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Da Nang Branch:</td>\r\n<td>494 2/9 Street, Hoa Cuong Nam Ward, Hai Chau District, Da Nang City</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Ha Noi Branch:</td>\r\n<td>Block 1905-1906, 19th Floor, Keangnam Landmark Tower - 72, Pham Hung, Me Tri Ward, Nam Tu Liem District, Ha Noi</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tel:</td>\r\n<td><strong>08 5412 5016 | 0909 344 653</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Email:</td>\r\n<td><strong>sales@unigolf.vn</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tax code:</td>\r\n<td><strong>0312567210</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'About us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2016-12-01 04:51:13', '2016-12-01 04:51:13', '', 0, 'http://developerweb.pro/goft/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
