(18, 1, '2016-11-18 00:49:42', '2016-11-18 00:49:42', 'This is an example page. It''s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\r\n<blockquote>Hi there! I''m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin'' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\r\n...or something like this:\r\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://developerweb.pro/goft/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-18 00:49:42', '2016-11-18 00:49:42', '', 2, 'http://developerweb.pro/goft/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(19, 1, '2016-11-18 07:14:12', '2016-11-18 07:14:12', '<h2>Unigolf - Best Service For Booking Golf And In/Outbound Golf Tour In Vietnam</h2>\r\nVietnam now have 39 golf courses spreading along the country with many of them are designed by famous golf\r\n\r\ners like Greg Norman or Nick Faldo. Not only for golﬁng, Vietnam have the advantage as the destination of many\r\n\r\nwell-known tourist attractions: Ha Long Bay or Hoi An Ancient Town. Beautiful landscape, nice weather, challeng\r\n\r\ning yet well-designed golf courses, good food is making Vietnam now a perfect place for your next stop golﬁng\r\n\r\nholiday.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nUniGolf is an award-wining (Vietnam Best Inbound Golf Tour Operator 2015 by World Golf Award), Vietnam\r\n\r\nbased company specialize in providing golf services: tee-time reservation, golf tours, transportations, golf event\r\n\r\norganizing, and ProShop for golfers from in &amp; outside of Vietnam. As our company holding the best price for golf\r\n\r\nbooking in Vietnam, we are conﬁdently ensure that our customers will get the most competitive price for golf\r\n\r\ntours or tee-time reservation in Vietnam.\r\n<h3>UniGolf provide aﬀordable Vietnam golﬁng breaks - from beautiful courses in the North of Vietnam to Phu Quoc Island</h3>\r\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-30 " src="http://developerweb.pro/goft/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/map-918x1024.png" alt="map" width="549" height="860" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nn additional to the best rate of golf booking, our staﬀs have experiences and knowledge to understand golfer’s\r\n\r\nneeds as well as helping you to have the best golf vacations ever in Vietnam. Our company is also a members of\r\n\r\nIAGTO, a prestigious international golf tour operator association\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-33 size-full" src="http://developerweb.pro/goft/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/banner-footer.png" alt="banner-footer" width="1619" height="259" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Vietnam Golf Courses', 